{"tid":461404,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個消失左嘅味道","createTime":"2017-11-07T14:11:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T09:26:30.000Z","uid":135722,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"8ce464cc38ba21b446ee2c548d410db1201f3d38","tid":461404,"uid":135722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T14:11:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/07/221021_6d059d8d93f4fef47695e8c21630d918.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F221021_6d059d8d93f4fef47695e8c21630d918.jpg&h=405ebf8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一直都好鐘意食士多啤梨味 但係唔知幾時開始就再見唔到有得賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61b1e957421caffbeb8e5e224ea1fd1a9bd084e3","tid":461404,"uid":13288,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T14:22:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/07/222158_a271cb025e561029ebba4cfeef2426c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F222158_a271cb025e561029ebba4cfeef2426c2.jpg&h=002938fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔知叫咩名 我叫佢薄荷片<br />\n有冇人知邊度仲有得賣"},{"pid":"41a03a8c2c3f4e8dfad3f95dc3bdfe4bed01a93b","tid":461404,"uid":134636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T14:24:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/07/222158_a271cb025e561029ebba4cfeef2426c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F222158_a271cb025e561029ebba4cfeef2426c2.jpg&h=002938fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔知叫咩名 我叫佢薄荷片<br />\n有冇人知邊度仲有得賣</blockquote><br />\n我都想知，小學個時想買但係阿媽話貴冇買到，到我有零用錢個時已經冇得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"301170ada36a11256265fe8e22f17114f0fc8af6","tid":461404,"uid":10504,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T14:26:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/07/222610_53b56047bc61c059943a7ad60b15db7f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F222610_53b56047bc61c059943a7ad60b15db7f.jpg&h=055597bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依家好似重有得買 <br />\n但隻味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前真係好J"},{"pid":"358ac335c74fa022863aff685af32667e21e073b","tid":461404,"uid":13288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T14:29:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/07/222158_a271cb025e561029ebba4cfeef2426c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F222158_a271cb025e561029ebba4cfeef2426c2.jpg&h=002938fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔知叫咩名 我叫佢薄荷片<br />\n有冇人知邊度仲有得賣</blockquote><br />\n我都想知，小學個時想買但係阿媽話貴冇買到，到我有零用錢個時已經冇得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果陣好似10幾蚊盒 真係幾貴下"},{"pid":"3913448d6aff9cae430d03357828d657ca7ddd0a","tid":461404,"uid":39641,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T14:30:17.000Z","msg":"橙汁冰冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"106b4539ace2fbfa205dfaf48044e4bf1740be51","tid":461404,"uid":132507,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T14:30:19.000Z","msg":"Ritz 綠色包裝 正方形 芝士餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc2054a2a3561773c3effd64261dcd9c92829f4","tid":461404,"uid":134636,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T14:30:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/07/222940_da75c4423c7013412e24ac6adee117ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fuploa