d61fafad806e968f433dec1a2a","tid":461404,"uid":131980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T01:35:48.000Z","msg":"女仔體香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba7c1646d6a89664e2d68a4289c18244923792ea","tid":461404,"uid":132361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T01:43:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/07/222610_53b56047bc61c059943a7ad60b15db7f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F222610_53b56047bc61c059943a7ad60b15db7f.jpg&h=055597bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依家好似重有得買 <br />\n但隻味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前真係好J</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n超鐘意以前隻味<br />\n自從佢變咗under minutemaid 就差咗好多<br />\n依家得返日版會係好飲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.twmemory.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/twmemory3105.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twmemory.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F09%2Ftwmemory3105.jpg&h=67210b2c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇人記得佢有個online<br />\n係你去搵Qoo賺分之類嘅遊戲 唔係好記得<br />\n雖然記得又虧又難搵 但係真係童年回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43243b08a208a4d43a52886af600a6b29cdbed1","tid":461404,"uid":132361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T01:44:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男朋友陣味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n然後聞到類似嘅味道就會sad一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}